abstract_ssm: Karen Stamm participated in several women's reproductive rights campaigns and organizations during the 1970s and 1980s.  This collection consists of correspondence, reports, background papers, and publications related to her efforts with those organizations for reproductive rights and against sterilization abuse, particularly of low-income women and women of color.
